                    <lb xml:id="p2-l18"/>Herrn Nationalrath Alfred Escher in 
        <lb xml:id="p2-l19"/>
                    <placeName type="place" key="Zürich (Stadt)">Zürich</placeName>.</p>
      </div>
    </back>
